    BaseNetworkSpace<T>

    ComputationGraphSpace
    ComputationGraphSpace: Defines the space of valid hyperparameters for a ComputationGraph.
    ComputationGraphSpace.Builder  
    ComputationGraphSpace.VertexConf  
    DL4JConfiguration
    DL4JConfiguration: simple configuration method that contains the following:
    - MultiLayerConfiguration
    - Early stopping settings, OR number of epochs
    Note: if early stopping configuration is absent, a fixed number of epochs (default: 1) will be used.
    GraphConfiguration
    Analogous to DL4JConfiguration, GraphConfiguration includes a configuration for ComputationGraphs, as well as early stopping (or, optionally numEpochs) fields.
